TEXT 3816 3152 Left 2 ;RV1: Adjust so that voltage at OUTPUT is 1/2 of VCC\nRV2: Adjust for 40mA quiescent current through R16/R17.
TEXT 3720 3304 Left 2 !.MODEL BD139 NPN(IS=2.3985E-13 BF=244.9 NF=1.0 BR=78.11 NR=1.007 ISE=1.0471E-14 \n+ NE=1.2 ISC=1.9314E-11 NC=1.45 VAF=98.5 VAR=7.46 IKF=1.1863 IKR=0.1445 RB=2.14 \n+ RBM=0.001 IRB=0.031 RE=0.0832 RC=0.01 CJE=2.92702E-10 VJE=0.67412 MJE=0.3300 \n+ FC=0.5 CJC=4.8831E-11 VJC=0.5258 MJC=0.3928 XCJC=0.5287 XTB=1.1398 EG=1.2105 XTI=3.0)\n.MODEL BD140 PNP(IS=1.408E-13 BF=163.6 NF=1.0 BR=42.79 NR=1.0 ISE=3.58E-14 \n+ NE=1.5 ISC=4.093E-11 NC=1.45 VAF=64.2 VAR=100 IKF=1.077 IKR=0.2 RB=1.98 \n+ RBM=0.001 IRB=0.024 RE=0.063 RC=0.01 CJE=3.045E-10 VJE=0.697 MJE=0.344 \n+ FC=0.5 CJC=6.78E-11 VJC=0.526 MJC=0.404 XCJC=0.528 XTB=1.35 EG=1.21 XTI=3.0)
TEXT 3712 3504 Left 2 !.MODEL 2SD896 NPN(IS=1e-11 BF=120 VAF=100 IKF=5 ISE=1e-11 NE=2 RB=2 RC=0.1 RE=0.05 CJC=340p CJE=1.5n TF=10.6n TR=1u ITF=2 VTF=10 XTF=1 VJC=0.75 MJC=0.33)\n.MODEL 2SB776 PNP(IS=1e-11 BF=120 VAF=100 IKF=5 ISE=1e-11 NE=2 RB=2 RC=0.1 RE=0.05 CJC=480p CJE=2n TF=10.6n TR=1u ITF=2 VTF=10 XTF=1 VJC=0.75 MJC=0.33)
